OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,FFounder of CNN, Ted Turner has died
OL,6,Faged 87.
OL,8,FLabelled as a brash and outspoken
OL,9,Ftelevision pioneer, Turner launched
OL,10,Fthe news network in 1980.
OL,12,FCNN reported Turner's death on
OL,13,FWednesday, following a news release
OL,14,Ffrom Turner Enterprises.
OL,16,FTurner's biggest achievement was the
OL,17,Fcreation of CNN, the first 24-hour all
OL,18,Fnews television network.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
