OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778105470
OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,FThe idea came from his own frustration
OL,6,Fwith television news, as he often
OL,7,Fworked past 8 o'clock at night, when
OL,8,Fmost national news broadcasts in the
OL,9,FUS had gone off the air, and was in
OL,10,Fbed by the time his local stations did
OL,11,Ftheir own broadcasts.
OL,13,FHe took a chance by starting the
OL,14,Foperation to create a 24-hour network,
OL,15,Fliving above the Atlanta office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
