OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778105470
OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,FCNN's breakthrough moment came during
OL,6,Fthe Gulf War with Iraq in 1991. Most
OL,7,Ftelevision journalists had fled
OL,8,FBaghdad, warned of an imminent
OL,9,FAmerican attack. CNN stayed, capturing
OL,10,Fimages of a war's outbreak, with anti-
OL,11,Faircraft tracers streaking across the
OL,12,Fsky and correspondents flinching from
OL,13,Fthe concussion of bombs.
OL,15,FTurner owned several professional
OL,16,Fsports teams in the United States,
OL,17,Fdefended the America's Cup in yachting
OL,18,Fin 1977 and donated $1 billion to
OL,19,FUnited Nations charities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
