OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,FHe earned the nicknames "Captain
OL,6,FOutrageous" and "The Mouth of the
OL,7,FSouth" and once bragged "If only I had
OL,8,Fa little humility, I'd be perfect."
OL,10,FKnown for partying and wooing women
OL,11,Fwith a roguish charm, the lean,
OL,12,Fmustachioed sportsman married three
OL,13,Ftimes, most famously actor Jane Fonda
OL,14,Ffrom 1991 to 2001.
OL,16,FShe quit acting while married to
OL,17,FTurner, but tired of his philandering
OL,18,Fand divorced him, although they
OL,19,Fremained friends.
