OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778105470
OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,F"He was sexy. He was brilliant. He had
OL,6,Ftwo million acres by the time I left.
OL,7,FIt would have been easy to stay,"
OL,8,FFonda said of her relationship with
OL,9,FTurner.
OL,11,FHe was slowed in later years by Lewy
OL,12,FBody Dementia. Long since out of the
OL,13,Ftelevision business, he concentrated
OL,14,Fon philanthropy and his more than 2
OL,15,Fmillion acres of property, including
OL,16,Fthe nation's largest bison herd.
OL,18,FBorn in 1938 in Cincinnati, Turner and
OL,19,Fhis family later moved to Savannah,
OL,20,FGeorgia, where he grew up.
