OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,FAfter being expelled from Brown
OL,6,FUniversity for sneaking someone into
OL,7,Fhis room, Turner went to Atlanta to
OL,8,Fwork as an account executive for his
OL,9,Ffather's billboard company, Turner
OL,10,FAdvertising.
OL,12,FAfter his father's 1963 suicide,
OL,13,FTurner took over the company, later
OL,14,Fbuying an independent TV station with
OL,15,Fa weak signal that didn't even cover
OL,16,FAtlanta.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
