OL,3,CCNN founder Ted Turner has died aged 87
OL,5,FTurner was promised a continued role
OL,6,Fin CNN after his company's sale to
OL,7,FTime Warner in 1996 for $7.3 billion
OL,8,Fin stock, but was gradually pushed
OL,9,Fout, much to his regret. "I made a
OL,10,Fmistake," he later said. "The mistake
OL,11,FI made was losing control of the
OL,12,Fcompany."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FAnother of Turner's great loves was
OL,20,Fland.
