OL,5,FHe acquired millions of acres in
OL,6,Franches complete with roaming buffalo
OL,7,Fand was Nebraska's largest private
OL,8,Flandholder.
OL,10,FHe had a net worth of $2.5 billion in
OL,11,F2023.
